=Description=

By Graham Boyd, Founder of EvoluteSix:

"Can you imagine how we could transform our world if we combined the power of voluntary movements, where everyone contributes freely, with the power of capital backed business to put money to work?

It can be done. By emancipating our organisations, just as we have already emancipated real people. The first steps have been taken, for example Holacracy, Sociocracy and Deliberately Developmental Organisations. However, they depend on the grace of benevolent investors.

The time is right to re-design companies for the circular economy - governed by all stakeholders, not only by a privileged investor class. Enter the FairShares Multi-Stakeholder Organisation, where all stakeholders contribute to success, for all, because all stakeholders share the power to govern and the wealth generated."
(https://www.thinkdif.co/sessions/redesigning-your-economy-free-companies-that-cannot-be-bought-or-sold)

